It's not often that you hear of boxers giving back to a community, And in the south of Johannesburg, a boxing gym and its boxers are feeding the impoverished. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - It's not often that you hear of boxers giving back to a community. In the south of Johannesburg, a boxing gym and its boxers are feeding the impoverished. WATCH: Pollsmoor inmates get second chance in life with boxing It's nothing new as they have been doing it for three years now. Far too often many former boxers end up as charity cases, but at the southern suburbs recreation center in Johannesburg, It is the boxers that are being charitable to the homeless in their area. Watch eNCA's sports reporter Shahied Joseph's story in the video gallery above